WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Neon blood in the sky, we kiss the engine awake.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:11.450
Glass flowers erupt from the speakers, impossible and grinning.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:17.533
My shadow dances ahead of me, inventing new gravity.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:25.800
Everything burns gold for one ecstatic, unrepeatable second.

